name: Eula Lawrence (Genshin Impact)
description:
One of the playable characters from Genshin Impact. Trained on AnythingV3 and tested to work with other traditional anime models as well. Works reasonably with the more shaded/3D anime models also. Can also recreate her sword quite nicely on still poses.

Basic prompt:
anime drawing of EulaLawrenceGI with blue_hair and yellow_eyes and purple_eyes

For further away shots the second eye-color is not necessary:
anime drawing of EulaLawrenceGI with blue_hair and yellow_eyes


The two-tone eye color might need a little bit of inpainting but usually easy to get it right with just a few tries. When doing images from further away you can get away with just "yellow_eyes" to avoid unnecessary color bleeding that is common with diffusion models.

Recommended strength: 0.8-1.0

The clothing is a bit sticky so if you want to do variety you should do it in two passes where you first lower the strength of the lora and then inpaint the head back in with full strength.

modelVersions.name: v1.0
modelVersions.description: Recreates the clothing accurately. Could use some extended training to allow more variety and relax the model a bit, but the character consistency is really good at the moment.
